snippet.textDisplay:
Where I live, at least half of the girls on Tinder have either one of these two things in their profiles:
1) "Can you be the reason for me to delete my Tinder profile?"
2) "I didn't like to have my hair pulled when I was little. Oh how the times change."
Like... Really? That shit actually made me quit Tinder (and ironically, when I did that, I almost immediately met someone IRL).
